<!DOCTYPE subsection SYSTEM "mingle_help.dtd">
<subsection title="Create a new project from scratch" collapsed="true">
	<steps>
	<item><p>To create a new project, click the <link>New project</link> link on the <strong>Current projects</strong> page (the first page you see after installation or logging on - click the <strong>Mingle logo</strong> to display this page).</p>
		<screenshot alttext="Empty all projects page" src="resources/images/installation/create_new_project_link.png"/>
	</item>
	<item><p>Enter project name and select the 'Blank'.</p>
		<screenshot alttext="New project from template" src="resources/images/installation/all_projects_new_from_scratch.png"/>
		<hint>The <cref topic="project_settings_page">Advanced Options</cref> are already set with default values and are available for further project customization.</hint>
	</item>
	<item><p>Click the 'Create project' link to complete project creation.</p>
		<screenshot alttext="New project from template" src="resources/images/installation/complete_create_project_link.png"/>
	</item>
	</steps>
</subsection>
